#Create ConfigMgr package to recover deleted start menu and taskbar shortcuts

Follow the below steps to create a package in ConfigMgr to recover start menu and taskbar shortcuts.

Download both 

[AddShortcuts.ps1](https://github.com/microsoft/MDE-PowerBI-Templates/blob/master/ASR_scripts/AddShortcuts.ps1) 

and

[MpRecoverTaskBar.exe](https://aka.ms/ASRTaskBarRepairTool) to a folder.
